Package seedu.address.ui

Class UiPart<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • seedu.address.ui.UiPart<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActivityCard, ActivityListPanel, CommandBox, HelpWindow, MainWindow, ResultDisplay, StatisticCard, TaskCard, TaskListPanel
    public abstract class UiPart<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a distinct part of the UI. e.g. Windows, dialogs, panels, status bars, etc. It contains a scene graph with a root node of type T.
